Help us improve MAME

<p>
Our official roadmap is <a href="https://github.com/mamedev/roadmap">here</a> and some
of things listed are already implemented or in works. But we would like your input on 
these matters. So feel free to add new ideas by creating <a href="https://github.com/mamedev/roadmap/issues/new">issue</a>.
